# This example commits the generated CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md so a reader
# can see the build output without running `textus build`. In your own
# project you can choose either to commit or to ignore those projections.

# Local runtime artifacts — not source.
/.textus/audit.log
/.textus/notify.log
/.textus/last-build.log
/.textus/.last-build.json
/.textus/sentinels/
